Guidelines for contributing to mitorrent

Web sites related to the project and distribution:
https://www.aeyoun.com/projects/mitorrent/index.html (home)
https://pypi.python.org/pypi/mitorrent (packages)
https://github.com/Aeyoun/mitorrent (source)

mitorrent is licensed under the BSD 2-Clause License. By contributing your
code for inclusion, you agree to license your contribution and have it
distributed under the terms of mitorrentâ€™s license. A copy of the license is
included in the `LICENSE` file.

Any patches that add value and improve the project will generally be accepted.
Please, run the tests first (`python setup.py test && flake 8`).
